title: CNO, MCPON visit Pearl Harbor on Navy's birthday (The United States Navy)
text: ( Source : The United States Navy ) PEARL HARBOR, Hawaii ( NNS ) -- PEARL HARBOR, Hawaii - Chief of Naval Operations ( CNO ) Adm. John Richardson visited Joint Base Pearl Harbor-Hickam today on his first overseas tour as CNO, engaging with Sailors
